# Contents
The Final Project folder contains the data, Google Colab notebooks, machine learning output file, and PyLDAVvis.png visualization from topic modeling. It is orginized as follows:
*Project_Machine_Learning.ipynb 
*Project_Sentiment_Analysis.ipynb
*Project_Topic_Modeling.ipynb
*PyLDAVvis.png
*README file
*Predicted_data.csv
*ufo_sightings.csv
